plot: In the first episode of the second season of Bravo's 'The Real Housewives of Orange County' Slade struggles with jealousy as a result of Jo's partying, while Lauri is ecstatic after meeting George, the man of her dreams. Vicki attempts to teach her son Michael real world values while Jeana deals with her unruly household and her son, Shane's back injury. Meanwhile, Kimberly leaves Coto after a skin cancer scare and new housewife Tammy Knickerbocker joins the group.—Anonymous
